{"id":575432,"date":[{"year":1979,"month":1,"day":27}],"page":"4","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"","column":"","genre":"","count":"75","ytitle":"","mtitle":"更正","ftitle":"","authors":["华谢"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"编辑同志:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一月六日刊登的科学家小故事《用不着那么复杂》一文中，我把“容积”误译成“体积”。因这个外语词有体积、容积和容量等意义。请予更正。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"华谢"}]}